message: So, for Substandards we need to pick a venue, and a name. Vote now.

I need to sync with London, but I think the next Substandards will be on March 3rd. Last night was a lot of fun, so we'll continue in sync. Those who correctly realized that Pub Standards is really very similar to just going for a drink after work with your friends but giving it a name win no prize. But well done all the same.
yeah, I had a great time last night
